column2: SELECT     g.source_id, g.ra AS ra1, g.dec AS dec1, g.parallax, g.phot_g_mean_mag, g.bp_rp,    n.objid, n.distance,     s.ra AS ra2, s.dec AS dec2, s.u, s.g, s.r, s.i, s.z into mydb.gaia_sdss_phot_wd from MyDB.gaia_wds_loc AS g     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( g.ra, g.dec, #) AS n     JOIN Star AS s ON n.objid=s.objid
